Stupid people.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://rinkworks.com/stupid/">rinkworks.com/stupid/</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Check out that sight.  Pretty funny until you realize it's real stuff.<br>
<br>
Anywho, if some jackass was wondering around in RvR and their monitor suddenly went blank they would freak the fark out.  'OMG!  My computer crashed!  Ugh!  Oh no!  Tech support!'<br>
<br>
