<br>
I think Mythic needs to change their thinking and classify us as &quot;Offensive Tanks&quot;.  Light Tank implies that we're like diet coke or pepsi one itll taste kinda like the original but watered down and weak.  I hate that.  Basically all I really want is more base damage close to what zerkers had that includes all light tanks.  Our defense allows us to survive but just so very barely so let us have some offense.  Let Reavers do the &quot;supporting&quot; I'm their to chop some $#!% up let the pally support me for a change. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm18.showMessageRange?topicID=113.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm18.showPrevMessage?topicID=113.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm18.showNextMessage?topicID=113.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=38><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm18.emailToFriend?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm18.threadControl?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm18.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 bo